# Keep the app source and tests LF in the working tree regardless of
# core.autocrlf, so the smoke harness's LF-marker block extraction
# (tests/door-smoke.mjs reading index.html) and cross-platform diffs stay
# stable. A Windows checkout was silently rewriting index.html to CRLF and
# breaking the extractor.
*.html text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
